{"tid":44631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何教訓串嘴的小朋友","createTime":"2016-12-18T12:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T12:42:04.000Z","uid":67339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2817758b48f5377a32ed17f19895adbc47859c70","tid":44631,"uid":67339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:12:23.000Z","msg":"今日同個朋友行宜家，睇睡房時，有個小朋友勁串叫我地死開，我地循循善誘咁教佢要待人以禮，點知比佢老母話我地大蝦細😓<br />\n<br />\n大家認為要如何處理？"},{"pid":"25e41ec2e90154f9fc2c5ae0e882a3f887e13e01","tid":44631,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"同佢老母講<br />\n你唔教仔<br />\n就要預左佢比其他人教嫁啦"},{"pid":"13b9fcde885c9c0f7c577f1539bc8e45c9a24030","tid":44631,"uid":64417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:15:51.000Z","msg":"趁冇人車巴佢好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75664c39cebacce1819b19f3d0399cde359cd658","tid":44631,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:16:31.000Z","msg":"一巴車埋去"},{"pid":"2026ee5fe6f6645e51098d491c4fb09ef3dd9956","tid":44631,"uid":37022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一巴車埋去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再話你唔撚識教等我嚟教"},{"pid":"aa521a3f63498c9246aa5d08ceeb780e8681d3ca","tid":44631,"uid":11312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"樓主俾細佬恰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77f1224ac975d2e603fb1ae66ab72ffd7f7cc37","tid":44631,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:36:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主俾細佬恰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家真係唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲細路串過馬撚<br />\n老豆老母又唔教<br />\n我哋又唔可以打鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd406d84c060ac3a45b013bd4ffa3566c32c5c5b","tid":44631,"uid":14992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"咁撚細粒 好易唔小心撞飛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d0032569e15d06186170f152a42c746d0d3dcb","tid":44631,"uid":18545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主俾細佬恰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家真係唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲細路串過馬撚<br />\n老豆老母又唔教<br />\n我哋又唔可以打鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實應該直接打佢老豆老母<br />\n<br />\n子不教，父之過。"},{"pid":"154ac4b43fbbf772183c6ec2d5cc2cc0e35e99b2","tid":44631,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"示範返咩野叫大蝦細比佢睇"},{"pid":"1926e891830afff8676dca873607c50ac0555572","tid":44631,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:42:04.000Z","msg":"串贏佢"}]}